
LDAP Kit To-Do List
===================

   General
   -------
   * IPv6 Support: LKLdap and LKMessage needs to be updated to properly
     process IPv6 addresses if an IPv6 address is specified as the host or
     in the LDAP URL.
   * Add NSAssert() statements to test input data on the following classes:
     - LKBerValue
     - LKLdap
     - LKUrl

   LDAP Opeartions
   ---------------
   * Add LDAP rename methods to LKLdap and LKMessage.
   * Add LDAP whoami  methods to LKLdap and LKMessage.

   Documentation
   -------------
   * Finish README.
